wiiremotej
Class DrumCalibrationData

java.lang.Object
  wiiremotej.DrumCalibrationData

public class DrumCalibrationData
extends java.lang.Object

Contains calibration data for use in WRDrumExtensionEvents. Immutable. Be aware that if buttons are held when the controller is first connected (or the remote is turned on while the controller is plugged in), calibration data may be inaccurate.
